      "title": "'Bakery products will not increase prices'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President of the All Ceylon Bakery Owners' Association N.S. K. Mr. Jayawardena said.",
        "Mr. Jayawardena further said that the price of the bakery products will be borne by the relevant bakery manufacturer and the bakery owners will not be able to increase the price further."
      ],
